            "@type":"bpmn:ManualTask",
            "@id":"http://plex.org/manualtask_2",
            "dc:description":"Incubate mycobacterial suspension at 80 °C for 1 h in a water bath. This step will facilitate loosening of the mycobacterial cell wall and will also inactivate pathogenic mycobacteria."
